Package com.github.stupremee.mela.mongo

Class DocumentWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.stupremee.mela.mongo.DocumentWriter
  • public final class DocumentWriter
extends Object
    A class that makes it easier to write documents by using the BsonDocumentWriter. It stores all steps in a list and writes all the steps in the write method.
    Since:
    10.04.2019
